    slug: 'drunk-or-drugged-friend-what-to-do',
    title: 'What to Do If a Friend Is Drunk or Drugged: A Practical Emergency Guide',
    category: 'Young Adult Safety',
    excerpt: 'When a friend has had too much to drink or has been given something without their knowledge, knowing what to do can be the difference between a frightening night and a tragedy. This guide walks you through practical, potentially life-saving steps.',
    metaDescription: 'Learn exactly what to do if a friend is drunk or drugged at a party or event. Practical, step-by-step emergency guidance for young adults in any situation.',
